  description="Daca cauti top telefoane sub 500 lei, probabil vrei un dispozitiv functional pentru sarcini de baza, fara costuri mari. In 2026, piata ofera cateva optiuni decente in acest segment, focusul fiind pe autonomie si functionalitate esentiala."
  image="/images/articles/top-telefoane-sub-500-lei.webp"
  type="article"
  publishedTime="2026-03-12T08:40:36.174Z"
  modifiedTime="2026-03-12T08:40:36.175Z"
  author="Andrei Ionescu"
  faq={faq}
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <article class="article-page">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumbs">
